            "content": "{\"message\":\"Continuing STRIDE-per-process threats for remaining Process elements and starting Data Store elements.\",\"threats\":[{\"id\":71,\"element\":\"null_resource.clientid_replacement\",\"threat_description\":\"Malicious clientid_replacement script spoofs client ID in runbook causing misattribution.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Spoofing\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1556: Modify Authentication Process\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A07: Identification and Authentication Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Code-sign scripts; enforce script integrity checks; restrict execution hosts.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":72,\"element\":\"null_resource.clientid_replacement\",\"threat_description\":\"Script is tampered to inject incorrect or malicious runbook parameters.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1553: Subvert Trust Controls\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08: Software and Data Integrity Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Store templates in VCS; verify checksum before execution.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H\"},{\"id\":73,\"element\":\"null_resource.clientid_replacement\",\"threat_description\":\"Lack of audit for clientid_replacement leads to repudiation of runbook identity changes.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Log patch events with user and timestamp; forward to SIEM.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N\"},{\"id\":74,\"element\":\"null_resource.clientid_replacement\",\"threat_description\":\"Script exposes client secret or IDs in console or logs, leaking credentials.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02: Cryptographic Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Mask secrets; use secure variables; scrub logs.\",\