ript prints VM IP or credentials in console, leaking to logs.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02: Cryptographic Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Remove secrets from output; use environment refs; secure logs.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:C/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":80,\"element\":\"null_resource.file_replacement_vm_ip\",\"threat_description\":\"Script error prevents VM provisioning, causing operational DoS.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Test scripts locally; implement retries and failure notifications.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":81,\"element\":\"random_id.randomId\",\"threat_description\":\"Random ID generator is spoofed to produce predictable identifiers.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Spoofing\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08: Software and Data Integrity Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Use cryptographically secure random functions; avoid custom implementations.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":82,\"element\":\"random_id.randomId\",\"threat_description\":\"Tampering with random generator library yields collisions or weak IDs.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08: Software and Data Integrity Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Pin provider versions; verify provider checksums.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":83,\"element\":\"random_id.randomId\",\"threat_description\":\"Lack of tamper log means rogue modifications go undetected.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable provider audit logs; monitor changes to provider binaries.\",\"cvss_vector\"