ion of security rule updates.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable NSG flow logs and Activity Logs; store in immutable store.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N\"},{\"id\":89,\"element\":\"azurerm_network_interface_security_group_association.example\",\"threat_description\":\"Exposure of NIC or NSG IDs in outputs leaks network topology information.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02: Cryptographic Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Suppress sensitive outputs; use private IP references; restrict state sharing.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":90,\"element\":\"azurerm_network_interface_security_group_association.example\",\"threat_description\":\"Failed or delayed binding due to errors causes network connectivity issues (DoS).\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Validate terraform graph; implement retries; monitor binding status.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":91,\"element\":\"azurerm_cosmosdb_account.db\",\"threat_description\":\"Malicious alteration of DB account settings compromises regional failover or consistency.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A05: Security Misconfiguration\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable Azure Policy deny on account config changes; use resource locks.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":92,\"element\":\"azurerm_cosmosdb_account.db\",\"threat_description\":\"Lack of replication audit allows denial of unauthorized changes to Geo-replication ( repudiation).\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\