rage_container_vm\",\"threat_description\":\"No audit logging of VM container changes allows repudiation.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable logging; integrate with SIEM; enforce retention.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N\"},{\"id\":113,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_container.storage_container_vm\",\"threat_description\":\"Exposure of VM scripts to public due to misconfigured container.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02: Cryptographic Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Use private containers; authenticate requests; rotate SAS tokens.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":114,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_container.storage_container_vm\",\"threat_description\":\"Large VM script downloads or faulty code cause storage throttling (DoS).\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Limit download bandwidth; monitor usage; cache scripts locally.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":115,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob\",\"threat_description\":\"Blob package tampered to include malicious code binaries.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08: Software and Data Integrity Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Verify package checksums; sign blobs; restrict write permissions.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:M/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":116,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob\",\"threat_description\":\"Missing blob-level audit allows repudiation of code package changes.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable blob logs; forward to SIEM; enforce retention.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N\"},{\"id\":117,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob\",\"threat_description\":\"SAS URL or blob URL leaked exposing code package or credentials.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02: Cryptographic Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Use short-lived SAS; rotate keys; restrict blob to private.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":118,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob\",\"threat_description\":\"Frequent blob downloads slow storage account, causing DoS for deployments.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Use CDN in front of blobs; monitor metrics; cache packages.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":119,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob_front\",\"threat_description\":\"Front-end blob tampered to serve malicious scripts to clients.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08: Software and Data Integrity Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Validate front-end bundle checksums; sign assets.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:M/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":120,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob_front\",\"threat_description\":\"Absence of front-end blob logs allows repudiation of asset updates.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":null,\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09: Security Logging and Monitoring Failures\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable blob logging; route logs to SIEM; enforce immutability.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:L/A:N\"},{\"id\":121,\"element\":\"azurerm_storage_blob.storage_blob_front\",\"threat_description\":\"Public front-end blob allows attackers to retrieve outdated or